data.description: Check out this stunning home in the desirable Town Lakes Community in Lehigh Acres. This home is of great value open floor plan large kitchen with granite countertops and top of the line appliances. 3-bedroom layout, along with a loft and den for flexible living spaces, a Huge master bedroom and walk in closet. Master bathroom has him and her sink with nice bathtub jacuzzi. This home does have CITY WATER. Comes with alarm system, security cameras and outside sprinklers. Home overlooks the lake with a gorgeous view, is located on a corner lot along with 3 garages. Low HOAs! Grocery stores, shopping, and dining nearby! This home is perfect for families or anyone looking for a spacious and comfortable home. Centrally located and easy to show, Schedule your showing today!
